summary.blockquote:
This interface of this property is deprecated in the Navigation Timing Level 2 specification. Please use the
interface's read-only property instead.

remarks.para:
The legacy
PerformanceTiming.loadEventEnd
read-only property returns an unsigned long long representing the moment,
in milliseconds since the UNIX epoch, when the event handler
terminated, that is when the load event is completed. If this event has not yet been
sent, or is not yet completed, it returns 0.
